### Plotting gap compresses sequence identy across chromosomes using weighted averages to calculate sequence identity per window.
### Supports 1v1, 1v2, 1v3, etc.
### Below, we'll do 1v2. NIPT2T vs Y476h1 Y476h2.

# Basic usage.
bash weighted_seq_ident_calc.sh -ref NIPT2T.fa -query Y476h*.fa

# Alternatively written as.
bash weighted_seq_ident_calc.sh -ref NIPT2T.fa -query Y476h1.fa Y476h2.fa

# Run without options to pull up help page.
bash weighted_seq_ident_calc.sh
